<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien Cha chuh ka hita ie,
 A cha minsel pen chuh ka hi;
 Ka lung lauhna a um hiel puoi,
 Ka lungkhamna le a um puoi.

[V2]
 Lalpa Thagau panpih zala,
 Thihna dawngkawt ka kan tieng leh;
 Ka Pa'n naubang ei-sang tan tin,
 Dan muolpi khup viei viei tang ka.

[V3]
 2. Thihna dawngkawt lauhum tak chuh,
 Lalpen sepaih hangsan haw chun;
 Khandaih hiemtuok meikuong bang chun,
 Gitva bang ei heu zel una.

[V4]
 3. Thihna dawngkawt kihawn tieng leh,
 Vai bang thamlo dingin Lalpa;
 Thagau thiengtho Lamkai pen chun,
 Ziet-tieng chawn banin ei kai in.

[V5]
 4. Ka lungtup leh ka lunggulh cheng,
 Ka sep, ka bawl ka muolsuoh ma'n;
 Lalpa, Na thilbawl theihna chun,
 Nei panpih in, nei veng zelin.</lyrics>
<title>THE GATE OF DEATH</title>
<hymn_number>335</hymn_number>
<author>Zawmpau</author>
</song>